<h3 id="user-configuration">User configuration</h3>

<ol>
  <li>Your customers will need to have a Stripe account to receive the items</li>
  <li>With stripe connect active itâ€™s mandatory to be registered before posting an ad, this is controlled by the application.</li>
  <li>The publisher will be redirected to his profile to connect with Stripe.</li>
  <li>Once connected he will be able to sell items on your site.</li>
</ol>

